        public liquibase.statement.SqlStatement[] generateStatements(liquibase.database.Database database)
        Generates a DropSpatialIndexStatement followed by a DropIndexStatement, if applicable. The first statement allows extra clean-up when dropping an index. The second statement leverages the normal DROP INDEX logic.
